Package de.seggebaeing.sqlanalyzer.persistence.dto

Record Class LLMDTO

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.seggebaeing.sqlanalyzer.persistence.dto.LLMDTO
Record Components:
id - stable identifier
version - numeric value representing the modification state
name - non-null name
api - non-null provider identifier (enum constant name)
model - non-null model identifier
apiKey - non-null API key
minTemperature - minimum temperature value
maxTemperature - maximum temperature value
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Persistable
public record LLMDTO(int id, long version, String name, String api, String model, String apiKey, double minTemperature, double maxTemperature) extends Record implements Persistable
Data transfer object (DTO) for persisting an LLM configuration.

Holds identifier, version, and associated configuration fields. All string fields are non-null.

1.0
